pageContext.claim: “Domestic Terrorists have taken over Seattle, run by Radical Left Democrats, of course. LAW & ORDER!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is referring to a small area declared an "Autonomous Zone" in Seattle's Capitol Hill neighborhood -- which covers less than 1% of the entire city of Seattle, which is 142 square miles. The gathering was largely peaceful and was not attended by "domestic terrorists." The Capitol Hill Autonomous Zone was established on June 8 and cleared of occupants by police on July 1.
